![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/57cf4799-2b83-4111-805d-0bf6bc796a74/20240626_170248.jpg)

MJF tries to open Dynamite with a promo and gets interrupted IMMEDIATELY by the hometown boy, Daniel Garcia.

Garcia thanks MJF for saving him last week. Garcia says he's out here to do something nobody in the back has ever done...

He's gonna say NICE THINGS about MJF. Garcia was inspired by MJF's reign as World Champion. MJF had a conversation with Garcia where he said he saw Garcia as a pillar of the company leading to an embarrassing loss in a World Title match. This was motivation.

And for that.. He wants to thank MJF.

MJF says he was gonna ask Garcia to come out anyway.

MJF makes a challenge.

MJF VS DANIEL GARCIA AT WEMBLY STADIUM????

NOT SO FAST!

Ospreay IS HERE. Now Ospreay makes a challenge!!

DANIEL GARCIA VS WILL OSPREAY NEXT WEEK!!

INTERNATIONAL TITLE ON THE LINE. WORLD TITLE AS WELL IF OSPREAY WINS

MJF HAS BEEN OUTDONE?! AND HES NOT HAPPY ABOUT IT

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a298590b-d022-461d-9f6e-bf8444e2a502/20240626_170300.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/61fd940d-45b0-431a-8e1c-02cb03b0c7af/Screenshot_20240626-171830_TrillerTV.jpg)

Swerve Strickland watched the entire segment from the back.. He laughs at Ospreay putting a World Title on the line that isn’t his… Swerve sees Ospreay has a problem with focusing.

Ospreay better be focused when they team up in the main event tonight.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bfe5441d-2f75-483c-868b-13654757d05c/PhotoGrid_1_20240626173533.jpg)

*   ## **_LOS INGOBERNABLES DE JAPON DEF BLACKPOOL COMBAT CLUB BY DQ_**
    

CHAOS!!

Jon Moxley gets BCC disqualified when he starts swinging around a steel chair. Naito makes the unadvertised surprise appearance save for his LIJ stablemates..

Naito and Moxley brawl out of the arena and then Bryan comes face to face with Shingo Takagi!!!!

