![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/aef95ae0-c475-47d4-9518-1852ae2ed974/Screenshot_20240626-174211_TrillerTV.jpg)

*   ## **_OWEN HART CUP: JAY WHITE DEF REY FENIX_**
    

Christian Cage is out to confront The Bang Bang Gang after this excellent match. Christian wants the Unified Trios Championships for the Patriarchy.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/73986d78-cd18-41c9-ab06-2cebe697a780/Screenshot_20240626-175511_TrillerTV.jpg)

The Young Bucks announce that the Wild Card entree in next week’s Owen Hart Cup match against Jeff Jarrett has been selected by THE ELITE.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a97ec3e6-620e-46de-a12d-575eb0572d11/PhotoGrid_1_20240626180553.jpg)

The Acclaimed is cutting a promo about how they're going to win the AEW Tag Team Championships.

The Young Bucks challenge them to a six man tag at Forbidden Door but Billy Gunn called in a favor from a high place.

KAZUCHIKA OKADA'S LONG TIME RIVAL HIROSHI TANAHASHI WILL TEAM WITH THE ACCLAIMED AGAINST THE ELITE!!!!

SCISSOR ACE IS BORN!!!

