![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0278d793-603e-41a6-bf4a-4810fdeac256/Screenshot_20240626-181355_TrillerTV.jpg)

*   ## **_Mina, Toni and Mariah def Saraya, Anna Jay and Harley_**
    

Mariah May brought champagne in the ring for Toni and Mina to toast before their match Sunday.

They toast and they're dancing when Mina tries to smoke Toni Storm with the champagne bottle.

She hits innocent Mariah instead 💔💔💔

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a3fefd2f-2f06-4083-8b09-c16821b9e655/PhotoGrid_1_20240626182941.jpg)

*   ## **_"IM JUST HERE FOR THE YOUNG GUYS"_**
    
    ## **_\- Chris Jericho_**
    

Chris Jericho tried to get Minoru Suzuki to join his team at Forbidden Door against Samoa Joe, HOOK and Shibata.

Suzuki calls him a coward and challenges him to an FTW Title match instead.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f3d63b9b-e2c7-4474-b7bb-05a990260628/Screenshot_20240626-183839_TrillerTV.jpg)

*   ## **_ZACK SABRE JR. DEF. KYLE O'REILLY_**
    

Roderick runs into the ring to check on Kyle. ZSJ wants to get into it with Orange Cassidy when his TMDK boys show up.

Out comes ISHII to back up Orange Cassidy and all the while Gabe Kidd wants nothing to do with any of this stuff

